decks.notes: This deck focuses on utilizing aggressive creatures and burn spells to quickly take control of the board and deal damage to the opponent. The commander, Phlage, Titan of Fire's Fury, enhances this strategy by providing a powerful source of recurring damage. The deck includes a mix of creatures with aggressive abilities, removal spells like Swords to Plowshares and Lightning Bolt, and mana acceleration to help cast spells quickly. It aims to establish board presence early and maintain pressure on the opponent, using a combination of creature combat and direct damage spells to win the game swiftly. The deck is designed to be proactive and efficient, aiming to capitalize on its aggressive strategy to overwhelm opponents in fast-paced one-on-one matches.

This deck revolves around the commander Phelia, Exuberant Shepherd, and focuses on aggressive strategies to overwhelm the opponent in a 1 vs 1 Duel Commander format. The deck includes cards that support an aggro playstyle, such as creatures with efficient stats and abilities like Mother of Runes and Skyclave Apparition, as well as removal spells like Swords to Plowshares to eliminate threats from the opponent. The deck also includes cards that provide card advantage and protection, such as Stoneforge Mystic and Giver of Runes. With a strong creature base and a mix of disruption and protection spells, this deck aims to put pressure on the opponent quickly and finish the game before they can stabilize.
